<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR1b0001" type="notes"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Research Notes for 尚書</title><editor role="creator">TLS Project</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</p><availability status="2">This work has been licensed for use in the TLS</availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>Research Notes</title></bibl><p>Comments and notes to <bibl corresp="#KR1b0001"><title xml:lang="och">尚書</title></bibl>.</p></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2022-02-26T23:33:17.35+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Comments</head><p xml:id="KR1b0001-start"><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_018-2a.121" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2022-03-17T18:01:07.559+09:00">can in no way be regretted (to any effect?)</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_023-1a.32" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-07-22T17:56:17.109+09:00">孔穎達疏：，惟教人乃是學之半，言其功半於學也。Mayorov 225: [Ведь] наученье — ученья половина.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_023-1a.33" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-07-22T17:57:14.687+09:00">Когда в уме держать ты будешь начала и концы, чтобы они учения не нарушали,</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_023-1a.34" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-07-22T18:37:53.988+09:00">то добродетель твоя в красу придет, а ты того и не заметишь.</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_048-2a.80" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-07-22T20:35:27.981+09:00">舊注：言當先學古訓，然後入官治政。</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_011-2a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-28T22:03:20.716+09:00">Qian Zongwu 1990: ，欺骗老天</seg><seg corresp="#KR1b0001_tls_027-2a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2023-08-28T22:08:45.38+09:00">fails to/refuses to</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>